name: Stéphane Sbraggia
attachment: The article lists the names of the running mates (colistiers) of Stéphane Sbraggia, the outgoing mayor of Ajaccio, who is a candidate for re-election in the upcoming municipal elections. It highlights Sbraggia’s campaign team, which includes a mix of current municipal council members and new candidates from various professional backgrounds. The article emphasizes the diversity and experience of the team, aiming to represent different sectors of Ajaccio’s population. The announcement is part of Sbraggia’s broader campaign strategy as he seeks another term as mayor.
